IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User jadenprovost@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass emacs/gmail"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
AuthMechs PLAIN
SystemCertificates no
CertificateFile ~/.mail/certificates/ca-certificates.pem

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/Inbox
Trash ~/.mail/Trash

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* !Archive
Create Both
SyncState *
